snippet.title: Proportion - how to see if ratios are in proportion
snippet.description: Ratios are said to be in proportion if they equal.  This video looks at how to simply see if two ratios are in proportion - that is whether they are equivalent.  We then look at how to easily find out how much of a quantity is required to keep something in proportion.
